Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:43.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Woods... squirrel... lily... yellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:49.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your late father's friend\nlives so deep in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:51.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:57.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Welcome... I have been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:01:59.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A voice... from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:02.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't see anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:08.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been expecting you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:10.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:15.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You knew that I was coming,\NBokusen-Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:20.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've come to speak to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:22.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,about the swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:58.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,while I went in search for Kohaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:01.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku! What're you doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are poison insects!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wind Tunnel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:10.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:13.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're sucking in\nthe poison insects, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:20.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha, go after Sango and Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:29.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You sacrificed yourself and fought...\NYet I went after Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll kill you, then kill myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:49.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the only way\nto get you back from Naraku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:53.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me, Kohaku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop, Sango!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:15.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was my fault you ended up\nsucking in poison insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:20.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:22.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't look so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:30.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's still hope for Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:32.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:35.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:41.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:45.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:51.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Hang on! Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:58.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, we brought water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How is Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:06.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think he's much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is the information you seek...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:19.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,about the Tetsusaiga,\nyour father's heirloom sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A tree demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:26.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru, just what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:29.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A 2,000-year-old magnolia tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:30.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:36.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sheaths of the swords,\nthe Tetsusaiga and the Tenseiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:43.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that belonged to Sesshomaru's father\nwere carved from my boughs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sheaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:49.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So the sheaths for those swords\ncame from this tree!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:51.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The strange power of the sheaths...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see why after seeing him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bokusen-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:06:02.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You would know... the link between\NInuyasha and the Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean your younger brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's blood changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:14.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The first time was when a demon\nbit into the Tetsusaiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:18.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The second time, he had let go\nof the Tetsusaiga while fighting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:31.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:36.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This scent!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:47.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It changed from\na half-demon's blood scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:51.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to the smell of a demon's blood...\nlike mine and my father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The same smell of blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:57.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:06.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is a half-demon,\nborn between a demon and a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:09.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He could never become\na full-fledged demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru... there is something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:17.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that you, a full-fledged demon,\ncan do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:20.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but which Inuyasha could never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:23.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha could never do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:27.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is to maintain oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maintain oneself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For example, Sesshomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:41.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,during a battle, if you are cornered,\nyou are able to remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:44.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You never lose control of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:49.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I would never get into\nsuch a desperate situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:51.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:56.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, Inuyasha is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:00.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If backed into a corner\nand his life is in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in order to protect his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:06.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,his demon blood takes control\nof the body and transforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's what happened that time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:13.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:20.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the pure demon blood of his father\nis too strong for a half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:24.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:29.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It could be said that the demon blood\ndevours the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He cannot recognize himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:37.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He cannot differentiate between\nfriend or foe... He just kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:44.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And in that transformation\NInuyasha will eventually lose his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:50.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He will become a demon\nwho only knows how to fight and kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:53.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He will continue to fight\nuntil he is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:06.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your father probably did not want\nsuch a fate for Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:12.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is why he bequeathed Inuyasha\nthe Tetsusaiga to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tetsusaiga protects him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:19.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he lets go of that sword,\NInuyasha becomes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:28.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, you've really matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaddya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:32.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm complimenting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:35.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You saved Kohaku's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:39.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just wanted to irritate Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:44.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we get Kohaku back alive\nthat would make Naraku mad as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:46.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Putting on an act again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:51.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And besides, you were alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:53.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:57.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Did you worry?\N- Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was a bit concerned, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:03.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,since you didn't come for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:08.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Doesn't your wound hurt?\NLemme see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:11.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Never mind.\NI can take care of it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you know you can\nmake it worse with lack of care?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- It's okay!\N- It's not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- I said I'm all right!\N- You're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:20.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Am, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:24.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry! I wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Thank us for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kagome and Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:33.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,for staying with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:34.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll get out of your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:39.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Staying by her? Why wouldn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:59.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It came from over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:05.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Gramps... My gramps!\N- Is it a demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:10.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is it, old man?!\NWhere'd the demon go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't sense any demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:25.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Over here! Over here! I tripped...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:28.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:31.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:37.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cripes! I thought a demon attacked.\NGetting us all worked up over nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good thing, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:45.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I twisted my ankle and had fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:48.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And now, you even carry me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, no. It's on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:53.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:55.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Right, Inuyasha?\N- Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:58.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:11:59.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Take care.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:14.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sis...\NAnd Mr. Dog-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dog-Man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:16.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As thanks,\NI'm giving you my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:30.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- What did he give you?\N- A snake's molted skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:33.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! A molted skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:37.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! Inuyasha, can I have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:47.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dang! We have no time\nto be saving people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we're walking this route anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:54.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whenever you do a good deed,\nyou become ill-tempered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ha!\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:58.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:02.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I smell human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:03.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:05.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I smell a lot of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:10.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that in the direction\nof that kid's village?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They've been attacked!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:34.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:35.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please help...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:41.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Kagome, take care of the kid.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:45.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Sango, stay and protect Kagome.\N- Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:48.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Let's hurry, Miroku!\N- Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I like this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:14.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll camp out here\nuntil the food runs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:16.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gather the women in one place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:19.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you try to escape, we'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Roving bandits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:27.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take care of you small fry later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's your leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:39.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, among the bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:41.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... I smell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's a demon in their midst.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:56.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kid... you have an interesting sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,controlling a bunch of bandits?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The leader is a demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:13.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kid... hand over that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! What're you mumbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if I'm gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:32.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you won't hand over that sword\NI'll take it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:36.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sounds fun to me! Take it if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:42.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha still has difficulty\nwielding that sword. Will he be okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:48.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll cut the dirty hide\noff your back, demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:02.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Chief!\N- The Chief's giant hatchet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:05.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's a pretty sharp sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You understand?\NThen prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:15.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This calls for a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:20.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been showered\nwith my poison powder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:38.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:45.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An amazing sword!\NI like it more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:49.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:29.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Troublesome kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-that's!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:36.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:40.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:43.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Afraid, now that you know\NI'm a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:45.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:49.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A strong demon for a leader\nwill make us invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll continue to follow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:58.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Serves 'em right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:06.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a poison cocoon.\NIf you touch it, you'll melt away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:10.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The two inside\nhave totally disintegrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:27.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a poison cocoon.\NAnyone who touches it will melt away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even those two inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:33.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:46.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... so they've created a\nbarrier on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... can you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:53.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn... Of course!\NI'll rip apart this stupid cocoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:57.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:03.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems you can't move your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:08.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The poison powder has entered\nthrough your wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:11.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It will fester slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:16.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey... get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:17.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:20.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:23.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here you are, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:30.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tetsusaiga has rejected him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:33.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:39.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kid... what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:42.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why does this sword reject me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:48.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My sword Tetsusaiga... is choosy\nabout who wields it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:52.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It won't let a low-class demon\nlike you near it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:59.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this low-class bandit\nwas allowed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:02.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Low-class? C'mon, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:13.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see... kid.\NSo you're a half-demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:21.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A half-demon like you\nhad the gall...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:24.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to pick a fight with me,\nthe demon Gatenmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:30.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're late. Something must've\nhappened in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:35.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Are you all right?\N- I'm worried about Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:37.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:45.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha's wound\nis worsening steadily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:50.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn...the bleeding won't stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it because of the poison?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:58.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can barely maintain the barrier.\NI can't make a move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:03.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}However...\neven this barrier won't hold forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:07.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ah... Chief, this sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:12.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do as you please with it.\NI'm not interested in a sword I can't use!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:14.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:23.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That sword... I must...\NGet it to him somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:27.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a great sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:33.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time\nbefore the barrier wears off...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:36.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and the poison cocoon\nmelts them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:38.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I'll just sit here\nand enjoy the view.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:47.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bring on the women.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:50.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.55,0:21:53.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:01.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:51.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is badly hurt by\nthe poison moth demon, Gatenmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:54.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But his demon blood takes over...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.21,0:23:56.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and slaughters even the bandits\nwho beg for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:23:59.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can we reverse Inuyasha's\ntransformation?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:03.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, Sango...\NWe must think of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.95,0:24:04.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.05,0:24:08.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do we have to deal with\NSesshomaru at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.99,0:24:13.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Demon's True Nature"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:14.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
